🔑 Key Points
	•	NOW message: no msgScheduleAt → skip table check, just send.
	•	Scheduled message: always check table for freshness (preparedAt vs LastUpdatedTime).
	•	If table has no row → safe default is to send.
	•	If preparedAt < LastUpdatedTime → skip (stale).
	•	If equal or newer → send.

